\[
x(t)=\sum\nolimits _{i}\alpha_{i}\Phi_{i}(t)=\Phi(t)\alpha,\quad\alpha\in\mathbb{R}^{n}.
\]

\end_inset

Provided 
\begin_inset Formula ${\det\Phi(t)\neq0\text{ for all }t\in I,}$
\end_inset

